    "what bound it breached.The more sophisticated AI/ML models using neural network and deep learning are inherently black box models.",
    "They are used to detect anomalies but require additional support from eXplaianable AI (XAI) models to explain the decision made by the AI detector.",
    "However, both the ML and XAI models have individual accuracy limitations and this is compounded when used in combination.",
    "It also takes longer to train and test these models (see Section 5).",
    "On the contrary, explainability with the proposed GiBy detector is straightforward."
